onships and similarities for easy reference. An introduction to beach habitats and plant life, references for further reading, and a glossary of terms make this book fully useful for everyone who wants a good, general understanding of beach plant life and wildflowers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aSeashore plants - Texas. 0aSeashore plantszTexasvIdentification. 0aSeashore plantszTexasvPictorial works. 7aNATURE / Plants / Flowers.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/77115440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292757158423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292757158/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK